Hello everyone 3mptyb0x here! I’m the sheep inside the box.

Just another regular guy passionate about cybersecurity. You can find me active on many platforms (TryHackMe, HackTheBox, PentesterLab) under the same name. In this blog I try to give back something to the community by publishing various writeups. I hope you’ll find something helpful.
